#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int t,n,j=1;
	cin>>t;
	while(j<=t)
	{
		cin>>n;
		int a[n],r=0,f=0,i;
		for(i=0;i<n;i++)
		{
			cin>>a[i];
			r+=((a[i]/30)+1)*10;
			f+=((a[i]/60)+1)*15;
		}
		if(f==r)
		{
			cout<<"Case "<<j<<": Respawn Frag "<<f<<endl;
		}
		else if(f<r)
		{
			cout<<"Case "<<j<<": Frag "<<f<<endl;
		}
		else{
		
			cout<<"Case "<<j<<": Respawn "<<r<<endl;
		}
		j++;
	}
}
